AddPermission.name: AddPermission
AddPermission.description: Adds a permission to a queue for a specific principal.

ChangeMessageVisibility.name: ChangeMessageVisibility
ChangeMessageVisibility.description: Changes the visibility timeout of a specified message in a queue to a new value.

ChangeMessageVisibilityBatch.name: ChangeMessageVisibilityBatch
ChangeMessageVisibilityBatch.description: Changes the visibility timeout of multiple messages.

CreateQueue.name: CreateQueue
CreateQueue.description: Creates a new queue, or returns the URL of an existing one.

DeleteMessage.name: DeleteMessage
DeleteMessage.description: Deletes the specified message from the specified queue.

DeleteMessageBatch.name: DeleteMessageBatch
DeleteMessageBatch.description: Deletes up to ten messages from the specified queue.

DeleteQueue.name: DeleteQueue
DeleteQueue.description: Deletes the queue specified by the queue URL, regardless of whether the queue is empty.

GetQueueAttributes.name: GetQueueAttributes
GetQueueAttributes.description: Gets attributes for the specified queue.

GetQueueUrl.name: GetQueueUrl
GetQueueUrl.description: Returns the URL of an existing queue.

ListDeadLetterSourceQueues.name: ListDeadLetterSourceQueues
ListDeadLetterSourceQueues.description:
Returns a list of your queues that have the RedrivePolicy queue attribute configured
                                                with a dead letter queue.

ListQueueTags.name: ListQueueTags
ListQueueTags.description: Lists tags added to an SQS queue.

ListQueues.name: ListQueues
ListQueues.description: Returns a list of your queues.

PurgeQueue.name: PurgeQueue
PurgeQueue.description: Deletes the messages in a queue specified by the queue URL.

ReceiveMessage.name: ReceiveMessage
ReceiveMessage.description:
Retrieves one or more messages, with a maximum limit of 10 messages, from the specified
                                                queue.

RemovePermission.name: RemovePermission
RemovePermission.description: Revokes any permissions in the queue policy that matches the specified Label parameter.

SendMessage.name: SendMessage
SendMessage.description: Delivers a message to the specified queue.

SendMessageBatch.name: SendMessageBatch
SendMessageBatch.description: Delivers up to ten messages to the specified queue.

SetQueueAttributes.name: SetQueueAttributes
SetQueueAttributes.description: Sets the value of one or more queue attributes.

TagQueue.name: TagQueue
TagQueue.description: Add tags to the specified SQS queue.

UntagQueue.name: UntagQueue
UntagQueue.description: Remove tags from the specified SQS queue.
